snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 09 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 09 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 25th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: We Build Black Hole Making Machine -100% Real | Part-1
snippet.description:
Please Watch Part-2 Also. Everything You Will See In Part2 Is Real. NO Vfx or Graphics Are Used. Our Machine Will Create Something Which Looks Like Black Hole, Galaxy, Supernova, Universe etc.

A black hole is a region of spacetime where gravity is so strong that nothing, including light or other electromagnetic waves has enough energy to escape its event horizon. 

Our blackhole have also powerful gravity in the center and can pull a human size object inside the center.

#blackhole #mrindianhacker #science

(LYRICS ENGLISH TRANSLATIONS)

(Hook)

What’s up company (gang)
We Earning lotta money  
They think they are wise 
But they are too funny 
Don’t act like a bit*h 
We are they street OG’s
We know people from 
37,70 till 17 (Hood Pincodes in Mumbai)

(Verse 1)

Stop popping pills  
What’s up dawg are you different
Or should i teach you how to be 
Go anywhere but don’t f**k around here 
You wanna live in this country peacefully right ?
Or should i get your passport visa done 
Be aware 
Everyone is in thoughts 
How should i reach till Emiway Bantai 
We were Light in the Dark 
We ate from our  own plate
Didn’t steal from others plate 

Where are you ? 
Look here 
All my boys are roaming around 
Fearless 
One look all it takes to scare yall 
What do you want just tell me homie ? 

If your respect is important to you then 
Make sure you respect others too 
Or else will curse  you soo much that 
You will live your whole 
Life in fear 

Represting India 
One fight down 
Two fight straight to the grave 


(Verse 2)

(Mumbai slangs)
Its not lakhs its crore we talk 
Love is betrayal 
Soo make sure you 
Put you heart in right place 
You got one more chance 

If you fight  for yourself then world will say are wrong 
Either your sleep will be fulfilled or your dreams 

I’m speaking facts 
Who is supporting poor people 
There are no less rents anymore 
Weak people don’t have guts to change 
Their life 
We made it on our own 
That’s why we live life without worrying 

(Verse 3)

They are soft from inside 
But they act like tough outside 
Everyone is an artist 
No one is less than a criminal 
On the streets 
We changed to a good human 
Now we cruising with our parents 
We not scared of any tools or weapons 
We are only scared of god 

Leave this worldliness and go and hustle 
We are good human now but if it comes on us 
Then you better understand what will come to you 
My hood kid are more smarter than you 
Mom told work hard don’t choose wrong path 

If you don’t understand then just leave it 
Labels asking me for songs 
I gave them and took lot’s of money 
Now we gonna kill it with labels soon 

Knock knock on my doors 
Money coming faster 
Keep trying homie 
Don’t give up 
If you hustle today 
Tomorrow will be fun 
You will be successful 
Just keep going 

(Hook)

snippet.title: இது எனக்கு பயங்கரமான அனுபவம்😱| First Day in Mongolia | Tamil Trekker
snippet.description:
#tamiltrekker #mongolia #coldest 

Hey backpackers, get ready for my exciting Mongolia series. Here's my vlog for the first day, sharing my day-1 experience with -27 degrees Celsius. 

My new year's first international trip started in Mongolia, and you can't imagine the freezing weather that welcomed me! If you're looking for a pleasant season to visit Mongolia, I recommend visiting when it's less cold. 

Watch my latest travel vlog to learn about Mongolia's relationship with India, local travelling, and more.

********************

Please Subscribe Us & Share the Videos & Let others get informed about this channel 👉 http://bit.ly/TamilTrekker

​********************

நான் புவனி தரன், பேக் பேக்கர், ஹிட்சிகர், வோல்கர் & ட்ரெக்கர், உலகம் முழுவதும் பயணம் செய்து எனது அனுபவங்களை அனைவருடனும் பகிர்ந்து கொள்கிறேன்.

புதிய இடங்களைப் பார்ப்பது, வெவ்வேறு கலாச்சாரத்தை அனுபவிப்பது, மக்களைப் பற்றி அறிந்து கொள்வது, இந்த அழகான உலகத்தை தமிழ் ட்ரெக்கர் வழியாக உங்களுக்குக் காட்ட முயற்சிப்பேன்.

எனது இந்த பயணத்தில் அனைவரையும் வெளியே செல்லவும், ஆராயவும், அவர்கள் சந்திக்கும் ஒவ்வொரு சூழ்நிலையையும் சிறப்பாகப் பயன்படுத்தவும் ஊக்குவிப்பதாகும்.

I'm Bhuvani Dharan, Solo travel enthusiast, Backpacker, hitchhiker, vlogger & trekker who travels the world and shares my experiences with everyone.

My videos consist of my spontaneous everyday life as each day is a new adventure.

Love to see new places, experience different culture, learn about people, taste different food and more. I will try to show you this beautiful world via Tamil Trekker.

With an emphasis on traveling these vlogs are meant to encourage everyone to go out, explore & make the most out of every situation they come across.

​********************

நான் புவனி தரன், பேக் பேக்கர், ஹிட்சிகர், வோல்கர் & ட்ரெக்கர், உலகம் முழுவதும் பயணம் செய்து எனது அனுபவங்களை அனைவருடனும் பகிர்ந்து கொள்கிறேன்.

புதிய இடங்களைப் பார்ப்பது, வெவ்வேறு கலாச்சாரத்தை அனுபவிப்பது, மக்களைப் பற்றி அறிந்து கொள்வது, இந்த அழகான உலகத்தை தமிழ் ட்ரெக்கர் வழியாக உங்களுக்குக் காட்ட முயற்சிப்பேன்.

எனது இந்த பயணத்தில் அனைவரையும் வெளியே செல்லவும், ஆராயவும், அவர்கள் சந்திக்கும் ஒவ்வொரு சூழ்நிலையையும் சிறப்பாகப் பயன்படுத்தவும் ஊக்குவிப்பதாகும்.

I'm Bhuvani Dharan, Solo travel enthusiast, Backpacker, hitchhiker, vlogger & trekker who travels the world and shares my experiences with everyone.

My videos consist of my spontaneous everyday life as each day is a new adventure.

Love to see new places, experience different culture, learn about people, taste different food and more. I will try to show you this beautiful world via Tamil Trekker.

With an emphasis on traveling these vlogs are meant to encourage everyone to go out, explore & make the most out of every situation they come across.

snippet.description:
Basant Panchami 2023 : 
हिंदू धर्म में बसंत पंचमी का विशेष खास महत्व होता है. बसंत पंचमी हर साल माघ माह के शुक्ल पक्ष की पंचमी तिथि के दिन मनाई जाती है. बसंत पंचमी के दिन बड़े ही धूमधाम से मां सरस्वती की पूजा की जाती है. इस साल बसंत पंचमी का पर्व 26 जनवरी 2023 के दिन गुरुवार को मनाया जाएगा. मान्यता है कि विद्यार्थियों के लिए बसंत पंचमी का खास महत्व है. बसंत पंचमी के दिन विद्या और ज्ञान की देवी मां सरस्वती के पूजा करने से विशेष लाभ मिलता है

हिंदू धर्म में बसंत पंचमी का विशेष खास महत्व होता है. बसंत पंचमी हर साल माघ माह के शुक्ल पक्ष की पंचमी तिथि के दिन मनाई जाती है. बसंत पंचमी के दिन बड़े ही धूमधाम से मां सरस्वती की पूजा की जाती है. इस साल बसंत पंचमी का पर्व 26 जनवरी 2023 के दिन गुरुवार को मनाया जाएगा. मान्यता है कि विद्यार्थियों के लिए बसंत पंचमी का खास महत्व है. बसंत पंचमी के दिन विद्या और ज्ञान की देवी मां सरस्वती के पूजा करने से विशेष लाभ मिलता है

snippet.description:
ಬೆಂಗಳೂರಿನ ಕೆ.ಆರ್​.ಮಾರ್ಕೆಟ್ ಫ್ಲೈ ಓವರ್​​​​​ನಲ್ಲಿ ಹಣ ಬಿಸಾಡಿದ ವ್ಯಕ್ತಿ ವಿರುದ್ಧ ಕೇಸ್​ ದಾಖಲಾಗಿದೆ. ಹಣ ಎಸೆದ ವ್ಯಕ್ತಿಗೆ ಕೆ.ಆರ್​.ಮಾರ್ಕೆಟ್​ ಪೊಲೀಸರು ನೋಟಿಸ್​ ಕೊಟ್ಟಿದ್ದಾರೆ. ಹಣ ಎಸೆದ ಬಗ್ಗೆ ಮಾಹಿತಿ ನೀಡುವಂತೆ ನೋಟಿಸ್​​ನಲ್ಲಿ ಸೂಚಿಸಿದ್ದಾರೆ. ಇದೇ ವೇಳೆ ಮಾದ್ಯಮದ ಮುಂದೆ ದುಡ್ಡು ಚೆಲ್ಲಿದ ಅರುಣ್ ಪ್ರತಿಕ್ರಿಯೆ ನೀಡೋದಕ್ಕೆ ಹಿಂದೇಟಾಕಿದ್ದಾರೆ.

Farq Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 24th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Meri Baari | @IqlipseNova | New Hindi Song 2023
snippet.description:
“No matter where you come from, if you can dream about it, you can get it “

Says Iqlipse Nova as he presents a song that is an announcement and a celebration. Fresh off his viral single Mera Safar, singer-songwriter Iqlipse Nova is back with is latest drop, Meri Baari. With this one, he continues to tell his story about his dreams and goals in his own unique way.

#meribaari #iqlipsenova #merasafar #hindisong  #motivationalsong #newmusic #viral #trending #reels
Song credits : 
Sung, written and composed by Iqlipse Nova ( https://www.instagram.com/iqlipse_nova/?hl=en)
Music Producer : WhySoAryan
Backing Vocals : Harry Arora
Mixed by : Harry Arora

Video Credits : 

Producer : Vedaant Chaube
Director : Aditi Sharma ( https://www.instagram.com/aditi9sharma/?hl=en )
Asst. Director : Abhishek Choubey
DOP : Arun Sharma
Asst. DOP : Joshua
Costume Stylist : Aditi Sharma
Editor : Aditi Sharma & Shubham Vasudeo
Color Grading : Arun Sharma
Art Director : mansi savla & vrushali
Line Producer : Kishore Pawar
Production Manager : Pratik pawar
Production House : C21 Studio\
Cast:
Simran Sharma (Mother)
Abhishek Choubey (Friend)
Manya Dhawan (Girlfriend)
Pratik (Friend)
Vedaant Chaube (Friend)
Nova’s manager - Nitin Menghani
Special thanks Paritosh Anand.

Lyrics:
Do chaar hi yaar hai mere,
Apno se door yahan pe,
Ghar wale sath nahi hai,
Na hai mera pyar yahan pe,

Yun toh hai hota nahi,
Kuch bhi sahi, jo bhi main karu..  
Fir bhi hai mann ye mera, mane nahi,
Kyu hi main daru!

Khush rehne ki hai Bimari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aagayi hai meri baari.

Sapne dekhe jo kabhi the,
Poore kar lu main wo saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aagayi hai meri baari…

Maine maar dekha, maine thoda pyar dekha
Maine haar dekha, toota wo guitar dekha 
Beeti thi raatein meri Dilli ki sadko pe,
Pocket mein sikka le, Sapne hazar dekha…

Na piya daru, kabhi liya nahi Vape par, 
Deta main heart, apne hateron k hate par..
Label bhi rota mere gaano k han rate par 
Khali main hoon baitha phir bhi jaata nahi date par..

Gaana bhi toh Gaana hai na, 
Legacy banana hai na,
Time thoda kam hai, Netflix pe bhi aana hai na, 
Jo bhi hai bola mujhe karke dikhana hai na,
Aaane wale saalon, Maa ko mumbai bhi toh lana hai na.

Jana hai na, han mujhe kal world tirp pe, 
Plane mein raat, han meri subhe hogi ship pe,
Saans k jaise loon main shares har dip pe, 
Hoga zamana meri ungli k tip pe…

Khush rehne ki hai Bimari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aagayi hai meri baari.

Sapne dekhe jo kabhi the,
Poore kar loon main wo saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aagayi hai meri baari…

Meri Baari, Meri Baari
Aagayi hai Meri Baari

Meri Baari, Meri Baari
Aagayi hai Meri Baari

Ye Khumari, hai khumari,
Aagayi hai Meri Baari

Meri Baari, Meri Baari
Aagayi hai Meri Baari

Kaise main bhoolun abhi,
Maa ki wo baatein sabhi,
Chota sa ghar wo mera,
Apne mere, Galiyan meri

Toota dil bhi tha kabhi,
Yaad aaye college abhi,
Dilli ki sardiyon si,
Raatein nahi, hoti kahin!

——

Khush rehne ki hai Bimari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aa gayi hai meri baari.

Khush rehne ki hai Bimari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aa gayi hai meri baari.

Meri Baari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Hai Khumari,
Aa gayi hai meri baari.

Meri Baari…

snippet.description:
Watch #HotstarSpecials Taaza Khabar only on Disney+ Hotstar: http://www.hotstar.com/1260127221

Haseen Raat, soundtrack from Hotstar Specials’ Taaza Khabar. Sung by Dev Negi, music composed by Aditya Dev and penned by Rashmi Virag.

A roller coaster of emotions, comedy, romance, action and drama, Hotstar Specials’ Taaza Khabar is an all-in-one package. Marking the debut OTT debut of social media sensation Bhuvan Bam, the series is a modern-day tale that dismantles the boon and banes of miracles. Produced by Rohit Raj & Bhuvan Bam under the banner BB Ki Vines productions, directed by Himank Gaur and written by the duo Hussain & Abbas Dalal, the series is exclusively available on Disney+ Hotstar.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3676 - 24 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3676: Yellow Shirt Ki Problem
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta desired a shirt in color yellow. He was therefore quite concerned because he lacked one and it is compulsory for him to wear the shirt in the meeting. Taarak attempts to enter Iyer's home, but it is locked. Then he calls Babita and Iyer, but neither of them answers. Taarak then visits Popatlal's home. Taarak receives a yellow shirt from Popatlal, but it is too small for him. Taarak afterward visits the Bhide's house and other neighbors' homes to look for the yellow shirt. Watch the episode to know more.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3676, 24 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000206878

Farq Episode 27 Teaser - 24th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish

snippet.description:
#Preet is about love, connection & the emotions you feel when you find the One. Vinod Bhanushali presents Dhvani Bhanushali’s "Preet". A love song from her album #Lagan composed by Abhijit Vaghani and words by Shloke Lal. The beautiful love story weaved in this music video is written and directed by Advait Chandan.

Experience what true love sounds like with #Preet, out now on Hitz Music.

Stream the song right now on - https://bfan.link/preet

Also, to be a part of Dhvani Bhanushali’s song ‘Masoomiyat’ send in your masoom moments with your loved ones here -  https://forms.gle/HrTRyS23EXBJaBMj9


AUDIO CREDITS:
Music : Abhijit Vaghani
Lyrics : Shloke Lal
Singer : @DhvaniBhanushali, @AbhijitVaghaniOfficial
Guitars : Shomu Seal
Keys: Akshay Menon
Mixed and Mastered by Aftab Khan at Headroom Studio Mumbai
Mix Assistant Vatsal Chevli
Atmos Mix done by Aftab Khan at Headroom Studio Mumbai

VIDEO CREDITS:
Written and Directed by Advait Chandan
Featuring: Dhvani Bhanushali & Guneet Singh Sodhi
Project Executed by Waris Thakur 
DoP: Mayank Khurana
PD: Pravin Kadam

Assitant Hair – Harsha
Styling - Esha L Amin

Special Thanks: Rahul Nanda

Hitz Music (Team): Kamlesh Bhanushali, Bhavesh Bhanushali, Pooja Vora, Rajendram Akula, Aisshwarya Shety, Neena Dawer, Dinesh Bajaj,  Pratik Shah, Siddharth Hussain, Payal Nair, Alok Srivastava, Hayat Hussain, Dilip Ahuja, Ramesh Shirke, Dhruv Patel, Rudra Bhanushali, Hriday Bhanushali & Suraj Rajput
Hitz Music (Finance):  Prabhakar Jain

Preet song Lyrics -
 
Ve sacchiyaan pareetiyaan.
Tere naal ve. Tere naal Ho giyaan.

Naa dil mera haarne ka gham nahi.
Je tainu jeeteyaan.

Dariyaa tu meri nadiyaa ka ik din tujh mein Dubnaa.
Meri to haddon ki rahi ab to koi bhi hadd na Sajnaa.

Ve sacchiyaan pareetiyaan.
Tere naal ve. Tere naal Ho giyaan.

Naa dil mera haarne ka gham nahi.
Je tainu jeeteyaan.

Tu meri holi. Tu hi diwali. Saare tyohaar mere.
Mainu teri cheezein, dher saare lamhein, de de udhaar mujhe.

Ke tu hi taan ae.
Dariyaa tu meri nadiyaa ka ik din tujh mein Dubna.
Meri to haddon ki rahi ab to koi bhi hadd na Sajna.

Ve sacchiyaan pareetiyaan.
Tere naal ve. Tere naal Ho giyaan.

Naa dil mera haarne ka gham nahi.
Je tainu jeeteyaan.

Tu ghar ka hai pata, tu hi raastaa hai naa.
Tu dhun ki sargam taraane bhi tu hi hai naa.
Lage ke sadiyaan youn hi nikal tere sang mein.
Lage ke aasmaani si kahaani hai apni sajnaa.

Ve sacchiyaan pareetiyaan.
Tere naal ve. Tere naal Ho giyaan.

Naa dil mera haarne ka gham nahi.
Je tainu jeeteyaan.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/hitzmusicofficial

snippet.title: Bihaan की याददाश्त वापस लाएंगी Thapki | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 602
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

While Shraddha and Sankar are stuck posing for an artist under Vasundhara's request, Thapki prepares for a skit to revive Bihaan's memory. What is the plan and will she succeed?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Starcast:- Jyothika, Hareesh Peradi, Poornima Bhagyaraj, Sathyan, Nagineedu, Aruldoss

The film is about a headmaster converting a poorly run school into one of the best in the state.

Movie:- Tejasvini (Aramm)
Starcast:- Nayanthara, Sunu Lakshmi, Ramachandran Durairaj, Kitty, Vela Ramamoorthy

A little girl falls into a deep borewell, and her rescue becomes a huge professional and personal challenge for a collector.

Movie:- Mahanati
Starcast:- Keerthy Suresh, Dulquer Salmaan, Samantha, Vijay Deverakonda, Naga Chaitanya, Rajendra Prasad, Bhanupriya, Malavika Nair 

Savitri, the most admired actress from South Indian cinema, goes through various tragic incidents in her personal life. Unable to cope with depression, she eventually becomes an alcoholic.

Movie:- U Turn
Starcast:- Samantha Akkineni, Aadhi Pinisetty, Rahul Ravindran, Bhumika Chawla, Ravi Prakash, Ashish Vidyarthi

The plot revolves around the death of motorists who break a traffic rule at a particular flyover in Hyderabad and the subsequent pinning down of the culprit by an intern journalist and police inspector duo.

It covers a wide array of film news, reviews, interviews, celebrity life, gossip, scoops, red carpet, and trends. Lehren is the first and most widely viewed and recalled Indian Entertainment destination.
Lehren's engagement with Showbiz dates from 1987, when it introduced several film-based entertainment shows for India's then-emerging television industry. Lehren, today, has unparalleled reach across digital platforms and is a favorite destination for young, hip, and trendsetting entertainment enthusiasts.

लहरें से मनोरंजन का साथ 1987 से है जब भारत के तत्कालीन उभरते टेलीविजन उद्योग के लिए कई फिल्म-आधारित मनोरंजन शो पेश किए। लहरें, आज डिजिटल प्लेटफॉर्म पर पूरी तरह से और हर जगह फैला हुआ है। लहरें आज युवा, अभिलाषी और ट्रेंडसेटिंग मनोरंजन उत्साही लोगों के लिए एक पसंदीदा प्लेटफार्म है।
